                <div class="col-100">
                    <div class="blog__details-wrap">
                        <div class="blog__details-content">

                            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                            <p>
                                MintLynk is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our URL shortening and QR code services.
                            </p>

                            <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>URLs:</strong> We collect the long URLs you submit to generate short links and QR codes.</li>
                                <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We may collect anonymized data about link usage, such as click counts and access times, to provide analytics and improve our service.</li>
                                <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> If you create an account, we collect your email address and password for authentication and account management.</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>To generate short URLs and QR codes.</li>
                                <li>To provide link analytics and usage statistics.</li>
                                <li>To improve and maintain our services.</li>
                                <li>To communicate with you regarding your account or support requests.</li>
                            </ul>

                            <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
                            <p>
                                We do not share any personal data with third parties except as required by law or to provide core services (e.g., hosting, analytics).
                            </p>

                            <h2>Security</h2>
                            <p>
                                We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
                            </p>

                            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
                            <p>
                                You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data by contacting us at <a href="mailto:info@mintlynk.com">info@mintlynk.com</a>.
                            </p>

                            <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
                            <p>
                                We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.
                            </p>

                            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                            <p>
                                If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@mintlynk.com">info@mintlynk.com</a>.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
